channel.description: I have a folder of RuneScape's cache from April 5, 2007 that I found on my old computer. It is untouched and has not been modified since that date. It has the .IDX0 - INX36 on it. This is before godwars is released though.. Godwars came out August 2007. Does anyone want this, I have no idea what to do with it.
